{"tid":662642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[A3]奇異博士拎唔拎得起雷神個鎚？","createTime":"2018-05-12T15:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T16:42:56.000Z","uid":168865,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7cc1c2365743122447fe88d2d0f5ca2dc8b134","tid":662642,"uid":168865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:00:57.000Z","msg":"今日同女朋友行行街，傾起Avengers3 問起我雷神鎚點解冇人拎得起<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女朋友：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：根係有啦，Vision 佢拎得起喎，睇完冇耐唔就得啦？<br />\n女朋友：係喎，點解佢拎得起既？<br />\n(其實我都唔知，求其諗就答佢）<br />\n我：因為佢有粒石，所以佢都拎得起囉<br />\n女朋友：哦，原來係咁。係啵，DS 佢都有粒石喎，咁佢都拎得起㗎！？<br />\n我：係㗎，家燕媽媽都有粒，你去問下佢啦。<br />\n女朋友一巴車埋黎嬲爆爆走左去搭車搵家燕媽媽。<br />\n我點先可以氹返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真：Vision 佢可以拎起雷神鎚，係因為佢有粒石所以可以拎？如果係，咁DS 都有粒時間石係未都拎得起呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82abb867bf3ad3b5b4b911ec9fe3b4f9d0be4ae5","tid":662642,"uid":168865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1b320160e8e690bcad218f1551a4966d025da3","tid":662642,"uid":152790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"Vision 係電子野黎<br />\n就好似你放個鎚喺𨋢咁"},{"pid":"f2091f76b1375a7fa24099382a2e0587728ad3d2","tid":662642,"uid":8867,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45a412f517b42a8ea60f488f988410ab33ff9344","tid":662642,"uid":168865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a1b320160e8e690bcad218f1551a